      "message": "Patch Set 2: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve\n\n(1 inline comment)\n\nCould be improved a bit if there is a chance to do this.\n\nShould this constant be used elsewhere in the code?  I would suspect yes, but I'm not sure if it is easy to find out where.",
